<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽戈尔德夫人悉心地照顾着拇指姑娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你很小，所以我必须保护好你。”玛丽戈尔德夫人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天早上，她带着拇指姑娘去花园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘很喜欢坐在妈妈的旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“亲爱的孩子，给我一个玫瑰花籽。”有一天玛丽戈尔德夫人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，我很强壮。”拇指姑娘回答说，“我可以给你三个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘的帮助反而让园艺工作的时间更长了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是玛丽戈尔德夫人并不在乎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她为自己拥有拇指姑娘感到非常高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的女儿也喜欢帮忙煮饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拇指姑娘，帮我把盐拿过来。”一天煮饭时玛丽戈尔德夫人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个盐瓶很重。”拇指姑娘吓了一跳，“但是我一定行！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘把盐瓶推给玛丽戈尔德夫人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天气热的时候，拇指姑娘喜欢在水里玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天下午，玛丽戈尔德夫人在一个碗里装满了水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把碗放在窗台上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，拇指姑娘就在橡子壳做成的小船里开心地唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只蟾蜍在屋子外面跳着，它在玛丽戈尔德夫人的窗下停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那优美的声音是什么？”蟾蜍太太问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是从那个窗户传过来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，蟾蜍太太跳到窗户下面的一个花箱上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在一朵花后面看了一下四周，然后往上看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，原来是一个有着优美声音的小女孩儿。”蟾蜍说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她也非常美丽呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蟾蜍太太又来了花箱好几次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她很希望拇指姑娘能够和她的儿子结婚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘的床是半个胡桃核。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天晚上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽戈尔德夫人就会把花瓣放在胡桃核里作为拇指姑娘的被子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“亲爱的孩子，你今晚想要什么样的被子呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽戈尔德夫人总是这样问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“郁金香。”拇指姑娘总是这样回答，“郁金香是我的最爱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天晚上，拇指姑娘问：“妈妈，今晚我可以睡在窗户旁边吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我亲爱的女儿，为什么呢？”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想要看星星。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然可以。”玛丽戈尔德夫人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把拇指姑娘的床放在了一个打开着的窗户的窗台上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“亲爱的孩子，你让我觉得很幸福。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈帮拇指姑娘整理被子说，“晚安。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，你也让我觉得非常幸福。”拇指姑娘说，“晚安。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>此时，蟾蜍太太正躲在花箱里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她等待着灯光熄灭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的机会来了。”蟾蜍太太发出了癞蛤蟆的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跳上窗台，一把抓住拇指姑娘，跳走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈！妈妈！”拇指姑娘大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，一切都太晚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>